{"tid":408684,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"駁lan線問題求救","createTime":"2017-09-21T12:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T16:28:26.000Z","uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f044f8dbc518ebe62af1741d5fee3559766a62fc","tid":408684,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"近排入左部ps4，擺左係房入面同電腦一齊，想用lan線唔用wifi上網，router係廳，如果想插lan線係咪一定要買多條線，廳拉線去ps4度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b36a593e5adef3b21ca2fa3c35bbf8a8aa99919","tid":408684,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"homeplug,用電掣位帶入房"},{"pid":"8fe44a68f723b50c2d4d878506ca621795f40280","tid":408684,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>homeplug,用電掣位帶入房</blockquote><br />\n上網睇過，有兩個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.雖則唔洗拉線，但homeplug駁ps4係用lan線定點？<br />\n2.點樣detect到我原本屋企個網路？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c060f743b43509547bbcbb4ecd558a9aaf9d6f","tid":408684,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4ecd0bf80db113d51bb8d5d911d01694af65bb","tid":408684,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"兩個簡單choice :<br />\n1. ) 拉多條線<br />\n2. ) 買隻5 port switch 放響電腦果面，router 條lan cable 連去switch, 再由switch出PC同PS4"},{"pid":"cf19cf640a866d06178774497b92bfbbc3de4bd4","tid":408684,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>homeplug,用電掣位帶入房</blockquote><br />\n上網睇過，有兩個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.雖則唔洗拉線，但homeplug駁ps4係用lan線定點？<br />\n2.點樣detect到我原本屋企個網路？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhomeplug 要買一對"},{"pid":"a67c3f69749df420fb9ebf044e0f2089682e5e67","tid":408684,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:33:37.000Z","msg":"順帶一提switch 唔好買tp-link, 垃圾中既垃圾黎"},{"pid":"3ee98e7de477521678a3ae412f9138fe880f697c","tid":408684,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順帶一提switch 唔好買tp-link, 垃圾中既垃圾黎</blockquote><br />\nswitch好似唔錯 速度會唔會分細左？<br />\n<br />\nbtw有咩牌子好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好少前人討論"},{"pid":"2d55b37f130ca0fc6dbbb18fa0efa4c95f6c4cb0","tid":408684,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:52:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab963997b8fb401d8cb28637c80ca174f806734","tid":408684,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>順帶一提switch 唔好買tp-link, 垃圾中既垃圾黎</blockquote><br />\nswitch好似唔錯 速度會唔會分細左？<br />\n<br />\nbtw有咩牌子好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好少前人討論</blockquote><br />\nanyway 有件事要確定左先，你本身係有lan cable去電腦度架嘛？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我見你寫拉&quot;多&quot;條<br />\n<br />\n速度理論上有分細，但我諗你完全唔會feel到<br />\n牌子我會揀netgear, 但5 port switch我諗要求可以唔駛太高，tp-link以外既牌子都應該唔會太廢(屋村鋪通常只有tp-link賣)，唯一係要留意買唔買giga lan"},{"pid":"4ca523d6eea09a61da6139501cff3ad8be4cff80","tid":408684,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"anyway 有件事要確定左先，<span style=\"color: red;\">你本身係有lan cable去電腦度架嘛</sp