iga lan</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然有，冇理解錯應該係用電腦條Lan cable做switch，再另外買多兩條lan駁ps4pc？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nswitch睇過應該都會揀netgear，評價較好<br />\ngiga lan姐係拎黎代替原本個router？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngigabit LAN (sorry 我之前懶冇打bit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )係指d port位support 1000Mbps, 如果你隻router本身係出到gigabit LAN, 但隻switch只係行到100Mbps既話咁就會得返100Mbps<br />\n呢方面要睇你上網用緊咩plan, router用緊咩model[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n諗住買Netgear GS105E，應該係gigabit lan黎<br />\n但係要諗lan線邊隻好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪求9其買條就得？"},{"pid":"92a729a0a910ee462dca135e9382d9a98717f99c","tid":408684,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"LAN 線齊晒8條芯既我覺得已經好夠玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都係買由switch 去pc/ps4果條啫？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca41b27986f0c2f34a10e2b6eb7ed32af9d36053","tid":408684,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LAN 線齊晒8條芯既我覺得已經好夠玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都係買由switch 去pc/ps4果條啫？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5port夠曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係呀 意思係lan線果啲牌子 質地"},{"pid":"9c9ab000e3c828b372448d294666f4a63bd5aade","tid":408684,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LAN 線齊晒8條芯既我覺得已經好夠玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都係買由switch 去pc/ps4果條啫？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5port夠曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"colo